This is HarfBuzz, a text shaping library.

For bug reports, mailing list, and other information please visit:

  http://harfbuzz.org/

For license information, see the file COPYING.

### ARM-VITA Notes

Currently compiling with

```bash
export FREETYPE_CFLAGS=-I/usr/local/vitasdk/arm-vita-eabi/include/freetype2
export FREETYPE_DEPS="freetype2 >= 12.0.6"
export FREETYPE_LIBS="-L/usr/local/vitasdk/arm-vita-eabi/lib/freetype -lfreetype -lpng"

./configure --host=arm-vita-eabi --disable-shared --enable-static --prefix=/usr/local/vitasdk/arm-vita-eabi/ --with-glib=no

make
```

Autotools isn't looking at sdk path for libraries for some reason...

```bash
...
checking for pkg-config... /usr/local/bin/pkg-config
configure: WARNING: using cross tools not prefixed with host triplet
...
```
